Robert F. Chew https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_F._Chew 0 Robert Francell Chew (December 28, 1960 – January 17, 2013) was an American acting coach and actor. He was best known for portraying drug kingpin Proposition Joe on the HBO drama series The Wire.
